# PLATFORM CONTRACT v1.0.0

**Espelho Python Sistema:** `app/platform_contract.py`  
**Espelho Python Website:** `core/integrations/platform_contract.py`  
**DTOs Website:** `core/public_dtos.py` · **Mappers:** `core/integrations/mappers.py` · **Gateway:** `core/integrations/api_gateway.py`  
**Alias:** `ARQUITETURA_OFICIAL_DA_PLATAFORMA.mdc`

> Nenhuma IA inventa endpoints, webhooks, payloads ou slugs fora deste documento.

---

## 1. Autoridade e sync

Sistema Master (Tkinter) = fonte oficial. Website Django = consumidor. **Sistema > Website.**  
Proibido: Website acessar banco/arquivos do Sistema.  
Sync: Sistema persiste → POST outbound webhook → Website invalida cache/sitemap → Website GET public.

---

## 2. APIs v1 (unica convencao — paths EN)

Base gateway Sistema: `INTEGRACAO_API_BASE_URL` (ex.: `https://api.nexustransfer.com.br`)

### 2.1 Public (Website consome — Sistema expoe)

| Metodo | Path | DTO Website |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/v1/public/statistics` | `CoverageSummary` |
| GET | `/api/v1/public/locations/states` | `PublicLocation[]` |
| GET | `/api/v1/public/locations/cities` | `PublicLocation[]` |
| GET | `/api/v1/public/locations/airports` | `PublicLocation[]` |
| GET | `/api/v1/public/locations/hotels` | `PublicLocation[]` |
| GET | `/api/v1/public/locations/events` | `PublicLocation[]` |
| GET | `/api/v1/public/locations/partners` | `PublicLocation[]` |
| GET | `/api/v1/public/locations/hubs` | `PublicLocation[]` |
| GET | `/api/v1/public/locations/support-points` | `PublicLocation[]` |
| GET | `/api/v1/public/locations/{website_slug}` | `PublicLocation` |
| GET | `/api/v1/public/locations` | agregado opcional (gateway) |
| GET | `/api/v1/public/vehicles` | `PublicVehicle[]` |
| POST | `/api/v1/public/sync/locations` | sync fila |
| POST | `/api/v1/public/sync/statistics` | sync KPIs |

**Nao existe em v1.0.0:** `/api/v1/public/coverage/summary` — usar `/statistics`.

### 2.2 Inbound (Website → Sistema)

| Path | event | Aliases legados Website |
|------|-------|-------------------------|
| POST `/api/v1/webhooks/inbound/company.lead` | `company.lead` | `company-leads` |
| POST `/api/v1/webhooks/inbound/driver.application` | `driver.application` | `driver-leads` |
| POST `/api/v1/webhooks/inbound/reservation.request` | `reservation.request` | — |

### 2.3 Outbound (Sistema → Website)

Sistema emite para: `POST {WEBSITE}/api/v1/webhooks/outbound/` (`core/views_webhooks.py`)

Eventos: `location.created`, `location.updated`, `location.deleted`, `vehicle.created`, `vehicle.updated`, `driver.created`, `driver.updated`, `company.created`, `company.updated`, `lead.created`.  
`reservation.*` — nunca altera conteudo publico do site.

### 2.4 Private (portais legado)

8765 `/api/driver/*` · 8766 `/api/company/*` → migrar para `/api/v1/private/*`

### 2.5 Deprecados

`/estatisticas`, `/inbound/motoristas/cadastro`, `/api/inbound/company-leads`, `/api/outbound/coverage`, `/coverage/summary`

