## 3. Mapeamento Django ↔ Contrato

| DTO | API | Models Django (fallback local) |
|-----|-----|--------------------------------|
| `CoverageSummary` | GET `/statistics` | `EstatisticasCobertura` |
| `PublicLocation` | GET `/locations/{level}` ou slug | `Estado`, `Cidade`, `Aeroporto`, `Hotel`, `EventoLocal` |
| `PublicVehicle` | GET `/vehicles` | `CategoriaVeiculo` |

**WebsiteSyncFields (ORM):** `id_admin`, `website_slug`, `website_path` — espelham IDs e SEO do Sistema. Website **nao gera slugs** quando `id_admin` presente.

**Schema.org:** `{% schema_place public_location "Airport" %}` (Hotel, EventVenue) via `seo_tags.py` / `landing_seo.html`.

