## 7. Payloads publicos

### CoverageSummary (`/statistics`)

`contract_version`, `companies_active`, `companies_total`, `drivers_homologated`, `states_covered`, `cities_covered`, `operational_points_total`, `operational_points_by_type`, `vehicles_published`

### PublicLocation

`id`, `entity_type`, `nome`, `tipo`, `estado_uf`, `cidade_nome`, `endereco`, `website_slug`, `website_path`, `portal_publicado`

### PublicVehicle

`id`, `categoria`, `capacidade`, `bagagens`, `aplicacao`, `marca`, `modelo`, `foto`

### Inbound restrito

`company.lead`, `driver.application` (sem CNH/fotos — sigiloso local), `reservation.request`

Modo localizacao: `manual` | `network` (alias `rede` no Sistema).

